# PicoCTF

## Mod 26
Cryptography can be easy, do you know what ROT13 is?
cvpbPGS{arkg_gvzr_V'yy_gel_2_ebhaqf_bs_ebg13_GYpXOHqX}

### Solve
**Flag:** `picoCTF{next-time_I'll_try_2_rounds_of_rot13_TLcK0UdK}`

Added '13' to the value of each alphabet, such that 'a' {0} becomes 'n' {13} and so on to decrypt.

### New Learnings
Learnt how to decrypt an encrypted flag, in this case, rotating it by 13 values.
